<h1 id="game-mechanics">Game Mechanics</h1>

<ul>
  <li>Gravitational Planets</li>
  <li>Planetary Hopping</li>
  <li>Getting sucked into blackholes</li>
  <li>More to come!</li>
</ul>

<h1 id="what-i-used-to-build-the-game">What I used to build the game.</h1>

<p>Unity3d Game Engine: <a href="https://unity3d.com/">unity3d.com</a><br />
Piskel Pixel Art: <a href="https://www.piskelapp.com">piskelapp.com</a></p>

